---
title: Savoury Turkey Soup with Kale and Udon Noodles
description: The combination of thick udon noodles, dark green kale and turkey is great, but the addition of beef broth concentrate puts this dish over the top. It has a distinct character that’ll have you slurping down every last drop. Chili peppers pack some serious heat, so add with caution!
